   - NEW: `backend/src/modules/currency/currency.service.ts` (`findAll`, `findActive`, `findByKey`, `create`, `update`, `remove`)
   - NEW: `backend/src/modules/currency/dto/create-currency.dto.ts` + `update-currency.dto.ts`
   - NEW: `backend/src/modules/currency/currency.controller.ts` (CRUD + `/active` per §3.A)
   - NEW: `backend/src/modules/currency/currency.module.ts` (MongooseModule.forFeature, exports)
   - NEW: `backend/src/common/seed/currencies.seed.ts` (RUB/USD/EUR)
