## 8. Scope: 1 atomic TZ (NOT 3 separate TZs)

Bundled as one **TZ-102** because:
- All three fixes are minor scaffolds (~150 LoC backend + 1 LoC frontend).
- They share smoke-test verification surface (1 server restart).
- Splitting into TZ-102a/b/c inflates PR overhead for trivial changes.
- Single commit allows rollback as one unit if any sub-fix fails.

---

