## 11. Compliance with project conventions

- **New entity follows UnitModule pattern** — Controller / Service / Schema / DTO split matching §4.4 of `docs/paper-and-ink.md` (Catalogue primitives).
- **RBAC via `@Roles` decorator** — matches `UnitController.list` and `ProductModuleController.list`.
- **Audit logging via `@AuditAction`** — matches `UnitController.create` (`action: 'create', entityType: 'Unit'`).
- **Seed idempotency mirrors `UnitsSeed`** — try/find/create fallback per row.
- **Typecheck gate** — `pnpm exec tsc -p tsconfig.build.json --noEmit` is the standard backend compile gate, per `docs/add-new-page.md`.
- **Tests skipped at TZ-102** — backend integration tests deferred to TZ-103 when dashboard frontend switch happens.

---

## 12. Risk callouts

| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|
| Decorator rename breaks a CI-side caller | Low | `grep -r 'product-modules' . --include='*.ts' --include='*.json'` pre-commit; rename uniformly |
| Frontend service URL not in grep target | Medium | §7.5 verifies file path BEFORE write_file; commit blocked if grep fails |
| Currency seed race vs. concurrent test run | Low | Pattern matches `UnitsSeed` (proven idempotent in TZ-09) |
| Inventory summary `@facet` aggregation cost | Low | Top-N + count, single index scan per facet; perf tested in §7.3 |
| RBAC over-sharing (currency GET to `user` role) | Medium | Acceptable for TZ-102; tightening deferred to TZ-43 |

