## 14. Anti-scope (DO NOT do in this TZ)

- ❌ Do NOT reuse `Unit` entity for currency. Wrong domain fit.
- ❌ Do NOT add a `/api/currencies/rates/refresh` job. Post-TZ-43.
- ❌ Do NOT rebuild `ModulesPage`. Already works; URL swap is enough.
- ❌ Do NOT add cache headers / ETag. Default NestJS responses are fine.
- ❌ Do NOT add OpenAPI annotations. Project has none today.
- ❌ Do NOT split into three TZs. Atomic is cheaper.
- ❌ Do NOT touch `StorageItemService`. TZ-101 already shipped.
- ❌ Do NOT migrate the Mongo `productmodules` collection. It's just a slug change; data unchanged.

